des: The Mississippi River borders most of East Arkansas; it’s a beautiful place to visit if you love nature with plenty of lakes and rivers. Arkansas has over 223 golf courses. If you would like to get the latest news, check for available tee times or receive notifications on discounted merchandise, send us an email at voice it golf @gmail.com.
